lyrics:
Under the bright stars shining
Breathing in the gentle air
The world pauses here
In this sincere peace


Under the stars we dance
Without haste, without noise
Under the stars we dream
Our hearts beat with love


The wind cradles thoughts
And time seems to stand still
In the embrace of the night
All doubts fade away


And in the serene darkness
I discover the light within me
Under the stars shines
The essence of my truth


Under the stars we dance
Without haste, without noise
Under the stars we dream
Our hearts beat with love
